{"Name":"Marina Gardens Lane","ShortName":"Marina Gardens Lane","Description":"The upcoming Marina Gardens Lane (Plot 2) site spans 0.60 hectares and is expected to house around 390 residences alongside 150 sqm of commercial space. Situated right next to the iconic Gardens by the Bay, this new development promises stunning views of lush greenery and the Marina Bay skyline. Its prime location in the Marina South precinct also offers future residents a mix of city convenience and waterfront tranquility, making it one of the most coveted addresses for modern urban living.","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/8c825baf-e2be-4b4d-8aaf-6d528aef65a5","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/8c825baf-e2be-4b4d-8aaf-6d528aef65a5","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}